In [660]:
from math import sqrt
In [661]:
    ytests=[]
    ypreds=[]

    
    loo = LeaveOneOut()
    
    for train_idx, test_idx in loo.split(x2):
        X_train, X_test = x2[train_idx], x2[test_idx] 
        y_train, y_test = y1[train_idx], y1[test_idx]

        model = Ridge()
        model.fit(X = X_train, y = y_train) 
        y_pred = model.predict(X_test)
        ytests.append(float(y_test))
        ypreds.append(float(y_pred))

    rr = round(r2_score(ytests, ypreds),3)
    rms = round(sqrt(mean_squared_error(ytests, ypreds)),3)
    print("R^2 Score:"+str(rr*100),"RMSE:"+str(rms))
